# Cortez45: Added for automatic reviewer assignment
# FIX Cortez49: Updated with instructions for configuring team handles
#
# These owners will be requested for review when someone opens a pull request
# that modifies code that they own.
#
# Order matters: later patterns override earlier ones.
#
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:
# 1. Create teams in GitHub: Settings → Teams → New team
#    - @your-org/backend-team
#    - @your-org/frontend-team
#    - @your-org/devops-team
#    - etc.
# 2. Or replace team handles with individual GitHub usernames:
#    - @username1 @username2
# 3. The handles below are placeholders - update before enabling CODEOWNERS
# ============================================================================

